The Football Champions of Italy have been crowned, with AC Milan claiming a 3-0 Serie A victory against Sassuolo. They only needed a point to secure the winning title on the ladder, with early goals cementing their path to victory. It's been 11 years since they held this title. Manager Stefano Pioli says he used NBA great Kobe Bryant as inspiration for his players. Overall, Milan scored wins in 26 of their 38 games.